r49151 | claus@wildside.dk | 2011-06-27 16:32:28 +0200 (Mon, 27 Jun 2011) | 9 lines

[CHANGE] Fluid FCE now uses Typoscript to determine available templates

To upgrade old FCEs, simply set Typoscript plugin.tx_fed.fce.templatePath 
anywhere, then edit your FCEs and re-select the proper FCE template file.

After this you can safely remove any FCE records and the tx_fed_domain_model_fce 
database table. Remember to clear all caches!


