[TER] 1.3.21

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r49100 | claus@wildside.dk | 2011-06-26 00:27:14 +0200 (Sun, 26 Jun 2011) | 17 lines

[FEATURE] Fully working SOLR AJAX service

This adds the first fully working, facet-supporting implementation 
and service for TYPO3 installations running SOLR. It allows zero-config 
usage or any of custom templates, layouts or Javascript search apps.

The ViewHelper lets you use this anywhere from Fluid, for example from 
a Fluid Template Display FE plugin.

The current service is solid but fairly low-level, requiring a search 
application - a default is included but in all likelyhood you will 
want to make your own adaptations.

Docs, VH: http://fedext.net/viewhelper-documentation/data-manipulators/solr-viewhelper/
Docs, Service: http://fedext.net/api-documentation/services/solr-javascript-service/


