[TASK] Improvements and cleanup in Fluid FCE related classes

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r48835 | claus@wildside.dk | 2011-06-19 01:11:49 +0200 (Sun, 19 Jun 2011) | 16 lines

[FEATURE] Initial version of new Fluid Template based FCE

This is the first, proof-of-concept-quality version of the 
quite special Fluid Template FCE implementation. It allows 
the creation of TemplaVoila-style FCE content which can 
be configured and rendered from a single Fluid template. It 
automatically creates a Flexform from the Fluid template FCE 
variables you register, making it EXTREMELY flexible, allowing 
for conditioned attributes and much more - already much more 
than what TemplaVoila FCEs are capable of doing.

Much more will happen to this feature shortly.

Documentation: http://fedext.net/guides/dynamic-fluid-fce/creating-a-fluid-fce/


