r48441 | claus@wildside.dk | 2011-06-07 20:39:42 +0200 (Tue, 07 Jun 2011) | 23 lines

[FEATURE] Major new feature: Extreme Debugging Suite

Complete overkill for debugging the entire request 
execution from Controller all the way down through 
any class you want to debug from down to all template 
rendering using a single, simple Service for it all.

Includes optional superclass for auto-debuggable 
ViewHelpers - which can be used during development 
and then switched off with no ill effect. 

Includes profiling with lap support for detailed 
profiling of loop execution times in any Extbase 
class in your extension as well as from within your 
Fluid templates.

Future plans: Graphed execution times and memory 
consumption etc. using ExtJS4 graphing features. 
With instant-replay type animation with control 
over the speed factor, naturally :) for all you 
control freaks out there.


